This is a simple twitter client just used to add a tweet in terminal.
It depends  on twitter4j,you can search it with google.

HOT TO USE:
1.If you first use it,it will create a config file:autotweet.conf
2.Then edit the config file with your personal information.
3.Then use it:
   java -jar autotweet.jar your status want to update.

**************************************************************
It support edit the Twitter API  Proxy,If you can't visit:
http://twitter.com you may need it especially in China.
Now you can use this API Proxy:http://nest.onedd.net/api/
**************************************************************
I write a shell to run it more simple:
tweet.sh
You can edit it according to your environment.


